ologist and may require sedation, neuromuscular paralysis, intubation, and mechanical ventilation in addition to the other measures.', 'Synergism', 'In general, the concomitant use of multiple serotonergic agents should be avoided if possible, or otherwise approached with caution if potential benefit is deemed to outweigh the risk.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/249894/', '', 'Rimegepant, Eptinezumab, Ubrogepant, Galcanezumab, Atogepant, Clonidine, Erenumab, Fremanezumab', 'Viloxazine, Esketamine', 1767369485);
